  "title": "DRAFTER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prepare, revise and update construction and as-built drawings based on project requirements</p></li><li><p>Produce 2D drawings using AutoCAD</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with engineers, project team and site personnel to ensure drawing accuracy</p></li><li><p>Update drawings according to site conditions and project changes</p></li><li><p>Perform other drafting and project support duties as required</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>5 years of relevant drafting experience</strong></p></li><li><p>Proficient in <strong>AutoCAD</strong></p></li><li><p>Willing to work at <strong>construction sites</strong> when required</p></li><li><p>Good teamwork and communication skills</p></li><li><p><strong>Bilingual in English and Chinese is an advantage</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Competitive salary commensurate with experience</p></li><li><p>Stable working environment and long-term career opportunities</p></li><li><p>Exposure to hands-on construction projects</p></li></ul>",
